description: Submission of a Validation Report  pursuant to condition 19 part B of planning permission ref: 164694FUL dated 01/09/2017 19  for'Phased redevelopment comprising a residential-led mixed use masterplan incorporating 1,965 residential units; 21,443 sqm. of flexible commercial and community floor space in use classes A1/A2/A3/A4/A5/B1/D1 and/or D2 including a two form entry primary school and nursery; a pedestrian / cycle bridge across the Grand Union Canal; car and cycle parking; site wide landscaping and associated works, including highway works; following the demolition of buildings and structures on the site (with the exception of the original elements of the Grade II listed Glaxo House). Buildings / blocks will range in height between two-storeys and 19-storeys. (EIA Application) (Departure from the Local Plan).'
